@DATABASE "Strider"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Strider"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                                  Strider
                                  =======



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Energy" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39942,60)"}         39942,60
@{"Energy = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41592,255)"}         41592,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
